            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "高盛將通過發債募資160億美元 在華爾街銀行中創紀錄",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"545\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EmKe17yfT7RG4L3kSbcvSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8162d04abf24bbd3f519655230567b72\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 高盛集團將通過發行投資級債券募資160億美元，這將是<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:華爾街;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/華爾街\">華爾街</a>銀行有史以來規模最大的此類發行。數小時前，該行剛剛公佈了大超預期的第四季度業績。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這筆交易還將成為2026年規模最大的美國高評級債券發行，繼華爾街六大銀行公佈季度業績後，這是周四該板塊推出的三筆債券發行之一。知情人士透露，摩根士丹利已啟動80億美元的發債交易，而富國銀行擬發債募資約50億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另一位因未獲授權公開談論此事而不願具名的知情人士稱，高盛此次發行分六檔，期限從3年至21年不等。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2bf4d0fa-7d78-3e16-acf8-cdc1aabf888a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"545\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RfsHkHsVP6K10rUa1cSKwA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/68bc23c0ce33aef2adfb56be6d6a0c52\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：高盛股票交易收入打破華爾街紀錄</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博匯編的數據顯示，在周四之前，高盛規模最大的債券發行是2022年一筆120億美元的交易。之前一年，美國銀行曾發債150億美元，當時是華爾街主要公司中規模最大的一次發行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛拒絕置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在借貸成本維持低位之際，銀行正加快融資步伐。摩根大通周三定價發行60億美元債券，拉開了該行業新一輪發行周期的序幕。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SdXedT9TeagfwYF9y8qCKA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/abbdfb4a0ad36f9a8d1929c6e72c02a0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman Raising $16 Billion in Record Wall Street Bank Bond Sale</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Ying Luthra、James Crombie.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E5%B0%87%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BC%E5%82%B5%E5%8B%9F%E8%B3%87160%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%9C%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-210236944.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-16 06:06:02",
